<br>
<br>
Now if I cant find any of those lets move on to fast pace zones where I can do a lot in a few hours. I've heard that if you get into a really good group in Unrest you can become rich and we'll lvled at the same time, in only a few hrs. Any ideas for that? And let's not get into one of those overcrowded zones where you can't quite kill a MOB without being KSed by a bat.<br>
<br>
Third problem of mine, where do I find all my words for my spells?(look below)I've heard that Treants drop almost everything, seeing one for the first time today I dont know if I want to mess with them. Anything near the Main Continents I could kill? Or are there any merchants that might sell the words?<br>
