My guest you are a high elf and can kill evil race. Take raft from oasis, you will enter Timerous Deep. Get off the raft when you arrive the beach. <br>
<br>
If you turn right and stay to the hill, you will arrive at the dock to Overthere. There is a single spawn ogre.<br>
<br>
If you turn left, there is a rock a very short distance up, there is another single spawn ogre standing on top of the rock.<br>
<br>
Both ogre is a 12 min spawn. Always spawn at the same spot and will not wander. Killing them will decrease the VS faction which is the overthere outpost faction. Each should give close to a bub blue xp all the way to lvl 24.<br>
<br>
There is a total 4 single spawn location if you look harder. Note never pull from the village, it will always be a double pull and sometimes Great Oowomp may tag along as well.<br>
<br>
By the way on the research, just forget it. At lvl 24 you buy an earth pet which is all I use to lvl 29.<br>
